    description         = 'This is the newer version of "stype 1.1.0",this ones version is 1.2.0.It is a simple module with six functions : "count_vowels" ,"count_consonants" "collect_vowels","collect_consonants","count_symbols","collect_symbols" which will count and collect out the vowels,consonants and symbols/punctuation in your string.Function count_vowels will count the number of vowels in you string. Function count_consonatns will count the number of consonants in your string. Function collect_vowels will collect the vowels. Function collect_consonants will collect the consonants.Function "count_symbols()" is used to count the number of symbols/punctuation.Function "collect_symbols()" is used to collect the symbols/punctuation.',
